由於你之前常處理 AML 相關的 SQL（CIF、ACCT、TRXN、SWIFT 等），以下是實務上最有用的查詢方向與範例。你可以根據實際 table 名稱調整。
1. 先確認相關 Table（建議先跑這幾句）
-- 找跟 AML screening / false hit 有關的表格
SELECT table_name 
FROM information_schema.tables 
WHERE table_name LIKE '%aml%' 
   OR table_name LIKE '%screen%' 
   OR table_name LIKE '%hit%' 
   OR table_name LIKE '%swif%' 
ORDER BY table_name;
常見可能表格：
	•	AML_SCREENING_LOG / SWIFT_SCREENING_RESULT
	•	PATRIOT_HIT / NAME_CHECK_RESULT
	•	TRXN / SWIFT_TXN / PACS_008 / PACS_009

2. 核心查詢：False Hit 統計（推薦先跑這個）
WITH FalseHit AS (
    SELECT 
        DATE(Transaction_Date) AS txn_date,
        COUNT(*) AS total_txn,
        SUM(CASE WHEN Is_False_Hit = 1 OR Hit_Result = 'False' OR Manual_Review_Required = 1 
                 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS false_hit_count,
        ROUND(100.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN Is_False_Hit = 1 OR Hit_Result = 'False' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) 
              / COUNT(*), 2) AS false_hit_pct,
        COUNT(DISTINCT Rule_ID) AS triggered_rules
    FROM AML_Screening_Log  -- ← 改成你實際的 table
    WHERE Transaction_Date >= '2026-06-01'
      AND Channel IN ('SWIFT MX', 'PACS008', 'PACS009')
    GROUP BY DATE(Transaction_Date)
)
SELECT * FROM FalseHit 
ORDER BY txn_date DESC;

3. 最常造成 False Hit 的關鍵字 / 名稱（非常重要！）
SELECT 
    Detected_Name,          -- 或 Matched_Word, Hit_String
    COUNT(*) AS hit_count,
    ROUND(100.0 * COUNT(*) / SUM(COUNT(*)) OVER (), 2) AS percentage,
    COUNT(DISTINCT Transaction_ID) AS unique_txns
FROM AML_Screening_Log
WHERE Is_False_Hit = 1 
   OR Manual_Action = 'Not Match'
GROUP BY Detected_Name
HAVING COUNT(*) > 5
ORDER BY hit_count DESC
LIMIT 50;
這會告訴你像 NEW YORK、BANK、TRUST 這些詞到底貢獻了多少 False Hit。

4. 特定 Rule 或 Module 的 False Hit 分析
SELECT 
    Rule_ID,
    Rule_Name,
    COUNT(*) AS hit_count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN Manual_Review_Required = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS manual_reviews,
    AVG(Processing_Time_Seconds) AS avg_time_sec
FROM AML_Screening_Log
WHERE Transaction_Date >= '2026-06-15'
GROUP BY Rule_ID, Rule_Name
ORDER BY hit_count DESC;

5. 前後對比（MX 上線前後）
SELECT 
    CASE WHEN Transaction_Date >= '2026-06-10' THEN 'After MX' ELSE 'Before MX' END AS period,
    COUNT(*) AS total,
    SUM(CASE WHEN Is_False_Hit = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS false_hits,
    ROUND(100.0 * SUM(CASE WHEN Is_False_Hit = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*), 2) AS pct
FROM AML_Screening_Log
GROUP BY period;

